org.jetel.graph.runtime.jmx

Interface NodeTracking

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeTrackingDetail

    public interface NodeTracking
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface for the tracking information about a graph node. This interface should be used by JMX clients. Each change of this interface (rename, delete or add of an attribute) should be reflected in TrackingMetadataToolkit class.
    Since:
    May 14, 2009
